        "title": "",
        "html": "<h2>Built to Last\n</h2><p>DNC HiVis workwear is crafted from premium, durable fabrics designed to withstand the toughest working conditions. Reinforced stitching and high-quality materials ensure long-lasting performance, while breathable fabrics keep you comfortable throughout your workday.</p>\n\n<p>Our range includes HiVis jackets, vests, shirts, and trousers, all designed to provide maximum durability and comfort.</p>\n\n<h2>Trustworthy and Reliable\n</h2><p>At DNC Direct, we believe in offering products that you can trust. Our HiVis workwear undergoes rigorous testing to meet Australian safety standards, guaranteeing you the best in safety and performance. Our commitment to quality ensures that when you choose DNC HiVis Workwear, you are choosing reliable, durable, and trustworthy workwear.</p>\n\n<h2>Great Value for Your Money\n</h2><p>We believe in providing top-quality HiVis workwear at competitive prices. Our collection offers a variety of styles and sizes to fit every need and budget. Each garment is meticulously designed to provide excellent value for your investment, combining longevity with unmatched comfort and safety features. Investing in DNC HiVis Workwear means investing in your safety and comfort.</p>\n\n<span id=\"dots\">...</span><span id=\"more\">\n\n<h2>Designed for Your Industry\n</h2>\n<p>Our HiVis workwear is tailored to meet the specific needs of various industries. From reflective vests to high-visibility jackets, our range ensures you find the perfect fit for your job requirements. Our dedication to excellence and customer satisfaction means you can rely on DNC Direct for all your high-visibility workwear needs.</p>\n\n<h2>Shop with Assurance\n</h2>\n<p>Explore our DNC Direct HiVis Workwear Collection today and experience the best in visibility, durability, and comfort. Shop confidently, knowing you are supporting a 100% Australian owned business committed to delivering superior high-visibility workwear. Join the DNC Direct family and experience quality, reliability, and unmatched safety.</p>\n\n<h2>Features and Benefits</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n<strong>High-Visibility Fabric:</strong> Ensures you stay visible in low-light conditions.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Reflective Strips:</strong> Enhance safety by increasing visibility.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Made from tough, long-lasting materials.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Breathable Fabrics:</strong> Keep you cool and comfortable during long shifts.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Reinforced Stitching:</strong> Provides extra durability and longevity.</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Meets Australian Safety Standards:</strong> Guarantees top-level protection.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<p><strong>Q: What sizes are available in the DNC Direct HiVis Workwear Collection?</strong></p>\n<p>A: We offer a wide range of sizes to ensure a perfect fit for everyone. Please refer to our size guide for detailed measurements.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Is DNC HiVis Workwear suitable for all industries?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Yes, our HiVis workwear is designed to meet the needs of various industries, including construction, road work, and more.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: How should I care for my HiVis workwear?</strong></p>\n<p>A: To maintain the reflective properties, wash your HiVis workwear in cold water with mild detergent and hang it to dry. Avoid using bleach or fabric softeners. For further details, you may visit this link.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: Are the reflective strips durable?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Yes, the reflective strips are designed to withstand regular wear and washing while maintaining their visibility.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Q: What is your return policy for HiVis workwear?</strong></p>\n<p>A: We offer a hassle-free return policy within 60 days of purchase. With DNC Direct you have up to 60 days to return or exchange an unworn item. Please visit our returns page for more information.</p>\n\n</span>\n\n<strong><button onclick=\"myFunction()\" id=\"myBtn\">Read more</button></strong>\n\n<style>\n#more {display: none;}\n</style>\n\n\n<script>\nfunction myFunction() {\n  var dots = document.getElementById(\"dots\");\n  var moreText = document.getElementById(\"more\");\n  var btnText = document.getElementById(\"myBtn\");\n\n  if (dots.style.display === \"none\") {\n    dots.style.display = \"inline\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read more\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"none\";\n  } else {\n    dots.style.display = \"none\";\n    btnText.innerHTML = \"Read less\"; \n    moreText.style.display = \"inline\";\n  }\n}\n</script>"
      }
